<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Echoes of Time - Connect with Bhutan Trough Stories</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Echoes of Time</h1>
            <p>Connect with Bhutan through stories</p>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <a href="#highlights" class="btn">Explore</a>
                <a href="#about" class="btn">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- About Bhutan Section -->
    <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>About Echoes of Time</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="about-container">
            <div class="about-img">
                <img src="https://cdn.audleytravel.com/3526/2522/79/15978913-taktsang-monastery.jpg" alt="Bhutanese Culture">
            </div>
            <div class="about-content">
                <h3>Echoes of Time</h3>
                <p>Echoes of Time is a platform that connects people with Bhutan through stories. We are a team of storytellers who are passionate about sharing the stories of Bhutan with the world.</p>
                <p>With its stunning monasteries, dramatic landscapes, and warm-hearted people, Bhutan remains one of the world's most exclusive travel destinations, committed to high-value, low-impact tourism.</p>
                <h4>Know about Bhutan:</h4>
                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <h4>72%</h4>
                        <p>Forest Coverage</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <h4>200+</h4>
                        <p>Sacred Monasteries</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <h4>100%</h4>
                        <p>Organic Farming</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Highlights Section -->
    <section id="highlights" class="highlights">
        <div class="highlights-content">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Bhutan Highlights</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Here are some of the highlights of Bhutan that many people love to visit, they lack the history behind them.</p>
            <div class="highlights-grid">
                <div class="highlight-card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://image.brigitte.de/13752830/t/fP/v6/w480/r1/-/buthan.jpg" alt="Tiger's Nest Monastery">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Tiger's Nest Monastery</h3>
                        <p>Perched on a cliff 3,000 feet above the Paro Valley, this sacred monastery is Bhutan's most iconic landmark.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://www.tripointholidays.com/images/international/bhutan/exp_bhutan.jpg" alt="Punakha Dzong">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Punakha Dzong</h3>
                        <p>The most beautiful dzong in Bhutan, located at the confluence of two rivers with stunning architecture.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-card">
                    <div class="card-img">
                        <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.MOoK4F7tcQ5yB6f-w8kQvQHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain" alt="Bhutanese Festival">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3>Colorful Festivals</h3>
                        <p>Experience the vibrant Tshechu festivals with masked dances and religious performances.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/user/narration" class="read-more">Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    
    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Traveler Stories about Bhutan</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="testimonial-text">
                    Bhutan exceeded all my expectations. The landscapes are breathtaking, the people are incredibly kind, and the culture is so rich and preserved. It's truly a magical place unlike anywhere else in the world.
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-img">
                        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/32.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson">
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4>Sarah Johnson</h4>
                        <p>From Canada</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="testimonial-text">
                    Visiting Bhutan was a transformative experience. The emphasis on happiness over material wealth gave me a new perspective on life. The hike to Tiger's Nest was challenging but absolutely worth it!
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-img">
                        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/45.jpg" alt="Michael Chen">
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4>Michael Chen</h4>
                        <p>From Australia</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="testimonial-text">
                    The festivals in Bhutan are like nothing I've ever seen. The colors, the dances, the spiritual energy - it's all mesmerizing. Our guide was so knowledgeable and made the experience even more special.
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-img">
                        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg" alt="Priya Patel">
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4>Priya Patel</h4>
                        <p>From UK</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>